\toprule
\textbf{Deliverable} & \textbf{Due Date} & \textbf{Days} & \textbf{Cost (USD)} & \textbf{Key Outputs} \\
\midrule
\endhead
Mapping \& Discovery & Feb 15, 2025 & 11 & \$4,400 & Comprehensive Mapping Report with visualized data and stakeholder insights.\\
Integrated Support \& Portfolio Strategy & Mar 31, 2025 & 11 & \$4,400 & Operational Plan and Portfolio Strategy Document, incorporating green, MSMEs, and AI pathways.\\
Portfolio Management \& Incubation Toolkit & May 14, 2025 & 11 & \$4,400 & Portfolio Management Framework; Incubation Toolkit (mentorship, peer support, capacity-building).\\
Follow-On Funding Strategy & Jun 12, 2025 & 7 & \$2,800 & Funder mapping and networking recommendations.\\
Egypt CO Model Enhancement & Jul 10, 2025 & 7 & \$2,800 & Technical Report aligning local needs with imaGen Ventures/ROTA methodologies.\\
Knowledge Products \& Technical Proposals & Sep 19, 2025 & 14 & \$5,600 & Two Knowledge Products; three Technical Proposals for funding.\\
Capacity Building \& Webinars & Nov 18, 2025 & 9 & \$3,600 & Four capacity-building sessions and three webinars with documented outcomes.\\
Results Framework & Dec 31, 2025 & 6 & \$2,400 & Final Results Framework Document with tracking indicators.\\
Ongoing Coordination \& Feedback & Throughout & 14 & \$5,600 & Regular updates, risk mitigation, iterative improvements.\\
\midrule
